{"id":941614213,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"4 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1682780992,"status":14,"status_display":"Time Limit Exceeded","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/941614213/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Make Array Empty","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    long long countOperationsToEmptyArray(vector<int>& nums) {\n        deque<int> dq(nums.begin(), nums.end());\n        priority_queue<int, vector<int>, greater<int>> min_heap;\n        for(int num : nums) {\n            min_heap.push(num);\n        }\n        long long count = 0;\n        while(!dq.empty() || !min_heap.empty()) {\n            if(dq.front() == min_heap.top()) {\n                dq.pop_front();\n                min_heap.pop();\n                count++;\n            } else {\n                int front_val = dq.front();\n                dq.pop_front();\n                dq.push_back(front_val);\n                count++;\n            }\n            if(min_heap.empty() && !dq.empty()) {\n                min_heap.push(dq.front());\n                dq.pop_front();\n            }\n        }\n        return count;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"make-array-empty","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
